Collaboration diagram for _FC_VarLSDynaIOInfo:

Detailed Description

Struct hold info about the file format for variable.

Description:

Need to keep filename, offset to data. Also info to decode "striped" data. (Striped = all data written for 1st element, then all data written for next element; non striped would have single data written for all elements, then next data written for all elements).

Set buffer size is o.k. because root names are limited to 75 char.

Modifications:

  • 7/18/2005 WSD Created.
